text: Khuda Babar is a Pakistani politician who has been a Member of the Senate of Pakistan, since March 2018. ==Political career== Babar was elected to the Senate of Pakistan as an independent candidate on general seat from Balochistan in 2018 Pakistani Senate election. He took oath as Senator on 12 March 2018. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Senate of Pakistan Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Khuda Babar
